body_html:
The _rebuild_tensor_v2 is new in master. Most likely you're using an older version of PyTorch to open a file saved from a newer version.

Save files are backwards compatible: new versions of PyTorch can open old save files, but the reverse is not always true.

body:
The `_rebuild_tensor_v2` is new in master. Most likely you're using an older version of PyTorch to open a file saved from a newer version.

Save files are backwards compatible: new versions of PyTorch can open old save files, but the reverse is not always true.
